/a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>对于长期活跃在VRChat的两人来说，这个VR空间和第三次亮相的Sanrio Vfes舞台就像家一样。两人在以熟悉的方式担任MC的同时，也将继续在现场表演中演唱标准歌曲。在《<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvQPlP0-enE" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>七层列车</strong></a>》中，观众被要求表演精心设计的动作，以营造一种团结感，而下一首歌《<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9uvVhwEj1Zw" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>不完美的存在</strong></a>》大受欢迎。</p><p>他们在展现比去年更加精湛的舞蹈表演的同时，也不忘记时不时地向观众喊话。前半段就像传递热量，后半段就像通过歌声传达文字。最后，歌曲《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B6c9wtENFgI" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>PROOF</strong></a> 》和《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D91jwPSEqpQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Find Yours</strong></a> 》唱得动情，触动心灵，留下深刻的印象，是一场非常令人满意的现场表演。</p><h2>富士葵</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>这是<a href="https://twitter.com/fuji_aoi_0618" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>葵富士</strong></a>第二次亮相Sanrio Vfes。一出现在舞台后面，她就演唱了《<strong>相关记忆</strong>》和《<strong>意大利餐厅</strong>》两首歌曲，用她有力的歌声瞬间点亮了会场。</p><p>富士葵在上届 Sanrio Vfes 上有力地演唱了“U”，但这次她翻唱了 Vaundy 的“ <strong>Kaiju no Hanauta</strong> ”。他们悠闲地走在花路上，高亢的合唱声回荡着，不仅两边的人都兴奋地叫喊起来，二楼的座位也发出了兴奋的叫声。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.z9bsrwgkazva-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.z9bsrwgkazva-1024x575.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.z9bsrwgkazva-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.z9bsrwgkazva-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.z9bsrwgkazva-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.z9bsrwgkazva-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.z9bsrwgkazva-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="575" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.fyzobnwa6sg9-1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.fyzobnwa6sg9-1-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.fyzobnwa6sg9-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.fyzobnwa6sg9-1-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.fyzobnwa6sg9-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.fyzobnwa6sg9-1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.fyzobnwa6sg9-1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.uxm0d88e3ypb-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loa