oads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7dbnrgkj4lum-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7dbnrgkj4lum-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7dbnrgkj4lum-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7dbnrgkj4lum-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7dbnrgkj4lum-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1wkxpu1s0jcn-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1wkxpu1s0jcn-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1wkxpu1s0jcn-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1wkxpu1s0jcn-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1wkxpu1s0jcn-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1wkxpu1s0jcn-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1wkxpu1s0jcn-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1ri61gwwh6yy-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1ri61gwwh6yy-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1ri61gwwh6yy-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1ri61gwwh6yy-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1ri61gwwh6yy-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1ri61gwwh6yy-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1ri61gwwh6yy-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7r7cgfl0bc4q-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7r7cgfl0bc4q-576x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7r7cgfl0bc4q-576x1024.webp 576w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7r7cgfl0bc4q-169x300.webp 169w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7r7cgfl0bc4q-768x1365.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7r7cgfl0bc4q-864x1536.webp 864w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.7r7cgfl0bc4q-jpg.webp 900w" width="576" height="1024" /></a></p><p> MC期间，他兴高采烈地向观众喊道“非常感谢大家的表情！”，而在接下来的“ <strong>Coke=High</strong> ”中，他以充满活力的舞台表演俘获了大家的心。我无法理解他说话和唱歌之间的间隙。</p><p>最后一首歌是“ <strong>Coyote</strong> ”。在她的现场表演中，很多人能够近距离看到她熟悉的舞蹈和舞步，都为之激动不已。在同一个 VR 空间中看到人们在你面前跳舞的机会并不多，因此对于那些计划参加时移表演的人来说，这是必看的。</p><h2> Buigoma（V 后藤真希）</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.tvudf27xe49q-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.tvudf27xe49q-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.tvudf27xe49q-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.tvudf27xe49q-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.tvudf27xe49q-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.tvudf27xe49q-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.tvudf27xe49q-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>第二天第一个出现在B3层的人是<a href="https://twitter.com/V_GOTO_MAKI" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>布伊戈马</strong></a>。后藤真希也是“早安少女组”的前成员，今年 15 岁，她从 2001 年开始穿越到过去，当她宣布将开始自己的职业生涯时，她成为了热门话题。 2023 年 10 月成为 VTuber。我做到了。 </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/10/9af9c8ecb68f84b9a3587cba152805f3-kix.yoaibxdbjsvm-300x169.png"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal">后藤真希 VTuber 出道！形象为“Buigoma”，一个穿越回 15 岁的 gomaki。</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2">前早安少女组。艺人后藤真希宣布将担任 VTuber“Buigoma”。 （来自 Maki Goto YouTube 频道）VTuber Maki Goto 穿越回了 2001 年 15 岁 [&amp;他...</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">VTuber</span> <span class="text-muted small ml-1">2023.10.25</span></div></div></div><p> Buigoma 的第一首歌曲是《 <strong>Ai no Baka Yaro</strong> 》。这是后藤真纪的个人出道歌曲，于2001年发行，当时她只有15岁。观众席上有几个声音在说：“哦！我以前听过这个！”</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.aawjwdvhocmu-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.aawjwdvhocmu-576x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.aawjwdvhocmu-576x1024.webp 576w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.aawjwdvhocmu-169x300.webp 169w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.aawjwdvhocmu-768x1365.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.aawjwdvhocmu-864x1536.webp 864w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.aawjwdvhocmu-jpg.webp 900w" width="576" height="1024" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.lgot2j3j2pdy-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.lgot2j3j2pdy-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.lgot2j3j2pdy-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.lgot2j3j2pdy-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.lgot2j3j2pdy-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.lgot2j3j2pdy-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.lgot2j3j2pdy-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.fwwdewwl4bmu-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.fwwdewwl4bmu-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1