索尼英语VTuber项目“PRISM Project”结束https://www.moguravr.com/prism-project-end/井文 Mon, 04 Mar 2024 01:43:38 +0000VTuber https://www.moguravr.com/?p=247151 <p>索尼运营的面向英语国家的 VTuber 项目 PRISM Project 宣布其活动将于 2024 年 3 月 31 日结束。从 4 月 1 日起，所有目前加入的 VTuber（总共 18 人）将保留他们的名字和“角色”。</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/prism-project-end/">索尼的英语 VTuber 项目“PRISM Project”结束的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p>索尼运营的面向英语国家的 VTuber 项目<a href="https://www.prismproject.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PRISM Project</a>宣布其活动将于 2024 年 3 月 31 日结束。所有目前隶属的 VTuber（总共 18 人）将从<strong>4 月 1 日起转变为个人 VTuber，保留他们的姓名和“角色”</strong> 。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1.webp"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-247153" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1.webp" alt="" width="1350" height="1350" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1.webp 1350w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1-1024x1024.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1-150x150.webp 150w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1-768x768.webp 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1350px) 100vw, 1350px" /></a></p><p> “PRISM Project”是AnotherBall Co., Ltd.于2021年推出的项目。成员是来自2120年未来的组织成员，主要活跃在YouTube上。该业务于2022年转让给索尼音乐娱乐公司（SME），该公司自此一直运营该项目。</p><p>属于“PRISM Project”的VTuber成为个人VTuber后，其当前的外观和各种帐户（X、YouTube等）的权利将转移给他们。每位成员计划于3月份在各自的频道上解释他们未来的活动政策。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en"> 【PRISM项目停止运营公告】</p><p>尊敬的 PRISMers，感谢大家的支持。PRISM 项目将于 2024 年 3 月 31 日停止运营。https <a href="https://t.co/XggbVLGeKE">://t.co/XggbVLGeKE</a> <a href="https://t.co/OCdCx8ATJh">pic.twitter.com/OCdCx8ATJh</a></p><p> — 棱镜项目 (@PRISMproj) <a href="https://twitter.com/PRISMproj/status/1763776242468139244?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 3 月 2 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>根据公告，原定3月份的活动将如期举行。各种商品的销售将于3月31日结束。虽然《PRISM Project》的官方 YouTube 频道和 X 账号将不再更新，但仍会作为档案继续发布。</p><p> （参考） <a href="https://twitter.com/PRISMproj/status/1763776242468139244" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X（旧推特）</a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/prism-project-end/">索尼的英语 VTuber 项目“PRISM Project”结束的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; 
泰国VTuber热潮目前陷入困境，追逐“文化熔炉”诞生的新人https://www.moguravr.com/the-kingdom-of-thailand-vtuber/すら Fri, 01 Mar 2024 10:00:25 +0000 VTuberARPタイ https://www.moguravr.com/?p=247054 <p>自“虚拟YouTuber”一词首次使用以来已经过去了七年多，VTuber文化在日本从年轻人到老年人广泛传播。这种VTuber文化正在逐渐向海外传播，体现了每个国家的独特个性[…]</p><p>这篇文章首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/the-kingdom-of-thailand-vtuber/">，讲述了从泰国 VTuber 热潮如火如荼的“文化熔炉”中涌现出来的新人才的故事</a>。</p> ; <p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-1024x768.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-1024x768.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-300x225.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-768x576.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-jpg.webp 1215w" width="1024" height="768" /></a></p><p>自“虚拟YouTuber”一词首次使用以来已经过去了七年多，VTuber文化在日本从年轻人到老年人广泛传播。这种VTuber文化正在逐渐向海外传播，并开始体现每个国家的独特个性。</p><p>在华语国家，类似日本氛围的VTuber文化已经扎根，而在英语国家，像VShojo这样尊重个性的文化正在形成。在拉丁美洲，独立VTuber（个人VTuber）的存在更为突出，而在韩语国家，具有浓厚K文化的音乐团体在国内外越来越受欢迎。</p><p>由于语言障碍，你可能没有太多机会每天看到这些 VTuber 文化。泰王国特别受欢迎，但知名度并不高。泰国的一个团体已经开始引起国内外的关注，目前正在成为一个非常热门的场景。</p><p>这次我想谈谈泰国深厚的VTuber文化。</p><h2 id="h.7fw8butz1gmd">从数据看与泰国的关系</h2><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-1024x547.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-1024x547.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-300x160.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-768x410.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-jpg.webp 1535w" width="1024" height="547" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.mofa.go.jp/mofaj/press/pr/wakaru/topics/vol154/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.mofa.go.jp/mofaj/press/pr/wakaru/topics/vol154/index.html</a></p><p>虽然我对国际事务不太熟悉，但我想简单谈谈迄今为止日本和泰国的关系。日本和泰国不是朋友，两国已保持<a href="https://www.mofa.go.jp/mofaj/press/pr/wakaru/topics/vol154/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">外交关系130多年</a>。</p><p>经济上，两国保持友好关系。例如， <a href="https://www.careerlinkfactory.co.jp/blog/thai-employment/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰国的日本餐馆数量不断增加</a>， <a href="https://www.clisk.com/web-marketing/thailand-inbound-promotion-20230823" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰国游客数量据说是东南亚最多的</a>。此外，在日本工作的泰国工人数量是 <a href="https://www.careerlinkfactory.co.jp/blog/thai-employment/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">所有国家中最多的之一</a>。从这些方面来看，可以说日本和泰国之间的联系非常牢固。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://youtu.be/vbSfqmS7va4?t=656" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://youtu.be/vbSfqmS7va4?t=656</a></p><p>从文化角度来看，泰国和日本有着密切的关系。漫画就是一个例子。可以毫不夸张地说，20世纪80年代，<a href="https://cir.nii.ac.jp/crid/1520009409094625280" target="_blank" rel="noopener">日本漫画渗透到泰国青年文化中</a>，成为构成当今日泰关系的元素之一。</p><p>根据集英社运营的海外服务“MANGA Plus by SHUEISHA”的<a href="https://youtu.be/vbSfqmS7va4?t=656" target="_blank" rel="noopener">读者统计</a>，泰国的用户数量排名第二。考虑到<a href="https://www.unfpa.org/data/world-population-dashboard" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰国的人口大约排在世界第20位</a>，你可以看到日本漫画和泰国之间的紧密联系。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-1024x575.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="575" /></a><br /> <a href="https://trends.google.co.jp/trends/explore?date=today%205-y&amp;geo=TH&amp;q=%2Fg%2F11byz8037n,%2Fg%2F11hznck6gj,%2Fm%2F0w68qx3,%2Fg%2F11f7r5y9lz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://trends.google.co.jp/trends/explore?date=today%205-y&amp;geo=TH&amp;q=%2Fg%2F11byz8037n、%2Fg%2F11hznck6gj、%2Fm%2F0w68qx3、%2Fg%2F11f7r5y9lz</a></p><p>然而，请记住，虽然日本内容在泰国很受欢迎，但它并不是单方面消费的。当我观看泰国VTuber的直播和视频时，我经常看到不仅来自日本，而且来自亚洲、英语国家和其他地区的文化共存。这种文化被描述为泰国vtuber行业的人将“<a href="https://premium.kai-you.net/article/759" target="_blank" rel="noopener">熔炉”描述为“文化熔炉”</a> ，这使泰国视频文化具有独特的吸引力。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://streamscharts.com/news/vtubers-viewership-q1-2023-japanese-streamers-continue-lead" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://streamscharts.com/news/vtubers-viewership-q1-2023-janpapanese-streamers-continue lead</a></p><p>从VTuber的角度来看，还有有趣的数据。根据` <a href="https://streamscharts.com/news/vtubers-viewership-q1-2023-japanese-streamers-continue-lead" target="_blank" rel="noopener">`Q1 2023&#39;&#39;在``流媒体图表&#39;&#39;发布的``vTubers实时流媒体收视率</a>&#39;&#39;中，该报告收集了分布平台的查看数据，泰国在VTUBER分布方面排名第三。</p><p>当然，这提出了一个问题，即如何确定VTuber的国籍，但是该统计数据非常有趣。尽管这不包括中国平台，但这对我来说是一个令人惊讶的结果，因为英语，中文，西班牙语和韩国语言在YouTube和Twitch上是突出的。但是，如果将其与<a href="https://twitter.com/VRchama/status/1622262309703024644" target="_blank" rel="noopener">瓦伦蒂诺·林戈（Valentino Ringo）的统计数据进行比较，瓦伦蒂诺·林戈（Valentino Ringo）收集了有关东南亚VTubers的专业信息，泰国是仅次于印度尼西亚的第二大国家</a>，您会看到来自Streams图表的数据纠正了。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.756t2veb7oi7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.756t2veb7oi7-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.756t2veb7oi7-jpg.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.756t2veb7oi7-300x168.webp 300w" width="768" height="431" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jtfwOCBx-Qs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jtfwocbx-qs</a></p><p>泰国也是基祖纳·AI（Kizuna AI）诞生Vtuber文化的地方，首先受到流行。它始于泰国，从韩国到美国迅速蔓延。在<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20230607083800/https://entamejin.com/column/archives/4396" target="_blank" rel="noopener">接受Activ8 Co. Ltd的首席执行官Takeshi Osaka的采访</a>中也涉及了这一点。</p><p>这不仅限于VTuber，但是在近年来音乐等其他内容中也可以看到类似的趋势。通过东南亚传播到世界的时尚似乎已成为一种趋势。</p><h2 id="h.13rug9540i3f">早期：从游戏评论员到Vtuber</h2><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.j5otpnugtc55-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.j5otpnugtc55-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.j5otpnugtc55-jpg.webp 640w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.j5otpnugtc55-300x169.webp 300w" width="640" height="360" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YbFgtVZikM8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ybfgtvzikm8</a></p><p>泰国在VTubers的历史上具有非常深厚的根源。</p><p>例如，“ Thequillmon”以<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YbFgtVZikM8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">第一个在Yua Fujisaki的影响下开始的泰国Vtuber</a>而闻名。在活动的早期，我没有打电话给Vtuber。该游戏在<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_slvmwj2OnM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2012年</a>发表了评论，在<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QGhDCc36ZsI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2017年</a>左右，当虚拟Youtuber仍在摸索时，它开始使用似乎是Mikumikudance（MMD）的3D模型，并且已更改为Vtuber。自从Vtuber黎明以来，Thequillmon是泰国Vtuber唯一的一家。它还提醒我，<a href="https://www.myholotv.com/talent/HORI_07" target="_blank" rel="noopener">霍里07</a>是马来西亚VTUBER机构的成员，属于已建立的“ <a href="https://virtualzeven.com/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VZ</a> ”。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdy5cb7qbh6b-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdy5cb7qbh6b-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1007px) 100vw, 1007px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdy5cb7qbh6b-jpg.webp 1007w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdy5cb7qbh6b-300x206.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdy5cb7qbh6b-768x527.webp 768w" width="1007" height="691" /></a><br /> <a href="https://vtuberthaiinfo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://vtuberterthaiinfo.com/</a></p><p>顺便说一句，在泰国，有很多案例将（转世）从旧的游戏评论员转变为Vtuber。粉丝们争辩说，在泰国VTUBER排名中应如何对待这样做这样的转世的VTubers。</p><p>例如，自2013年启动了实时视频以来， <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCompe4fS2oUss8CGTuhOSxA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">吉布里（Gibpuri</a> ）和艾托尔（Gibpuri）和艾托尔（ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGBkYTR4tMKS38TQHGWWLjg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Aitolh）</a>在<a href="https://virtual-youtuber.userlocal.jp/document/ranking" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UserLocal的粉丝数量</a>中排名很高。 Gibpuri在早期的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vJffGqdKDnc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">现场评论中以像现场评论这样的风格慢慢</a>发布，并且是Youtuber，是合适的Vtuber。</p><h3 id="h.u48nnwyotmsf"> 2019年：公司VTUBER的开创性“ AISHA”的出现</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DH0i7g77-jE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dh0i7g77-je</a></p><p>在泰国的VTUBER场景中，您一直想知道的是“ Aisha（Aisha）（ไอ）”。艾莎（Aisha）是AI猫形的虚拟偶像，旨在控制生物的命运，并从动画制作公司“ <a href="https://www.gaai.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Guardian Angel AI</a> ”中首次亮相。这是一家属于2019年泰国很少一家公司的VTUBER。我喜欢K-pop和动漫的歌曲，<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GdC4e3amqok" target="_blank" rel="noopener">我穿着3D Live Live Live on K-Pop风格的服装</a>，并唱许多<a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL-DEZKP7bdG5GzaYJ2yIVwkoFDE4LL0A4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">流利的日本封面歌曲</a>。</p><p>我喜欢挑战新事物，并且我的目标是与各种品牌合作。例如，我与泰国游戏“ Home Sweet Home：Online”<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2NqELyeEZrA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">合作</a>，有时在日本游戏现场视频中看到Aisha。</p><p>就技术方面而言，它在泰国VTUBER中尤其出色，周年纪念活动已经举办了<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OOBUouOQU5I" target="_blank" rel="noopener">3D音乐会</a>。对泰国的这种开创性计划和技术技能得到了高度评​​价，我们在“泰国社会奖项”的VTUBER类别中<a href="https://twitter.com/SocialAwardsTH/status/1496025185626955780" target="_blank" rel="noopener">赢得了“社交媒体上最佳影响者的表现”</a> 。</p><h2 id="h.ymonpokffjob">泰国的第一家VTUBER机构诞生</h2><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.2b73jg78gh9g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.2b73jg78gh9g-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.2b73jg78gh9g-jpg.webp 680w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.2b73jg78gh9g-300x220.webp 300w" width="680" height="499" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/Arcanis_Phriezt/status/1690019193863720961" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/arcanis_phriezt/status/16900191919193863720961</a></p><p>我还想注意Aisha所属的“<a href="https://www.plg.tv/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">多边形项目</a>”。该机构是与<a href="https://twitter.com/phriezt" target="_blank" rel="noopener">创始人“ Phrezt”</a>运营的“ <a href="https://www.matchlink.asia/business/page/Thailand/BANGKOK/79053-polygon-official-company-limited.html#google_vignette" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Polygon官方有限公司</a>”的项目。自从泰国开始蔓延以来，它一直很活跃，并且是关键人物之一。艾莎（Aisha）定位为该项目的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W7mKKsnlc-s" target="_blank" rel="noopener">第0代</a>，并已首次亮相到第二代。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-1024x543.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-1024x543.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-300x159.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-768x408.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-1536x815.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="543" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.plg.tv/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.plg.tv/</a></p><p> Polygon项目的第一个代表成员有许多VTUBER，上面有各种生物。例如，Lapine和Lucene是兔子，Zona是一只杀手鲸，Hoku是猫头鹰，Luxia是一个曲折的主题，这是一种有吸引力的设计，被日本VTUBER粉丝很好地接受。这次，我将介绍三个觉得他们正在做特别有趣的活动的人。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-1024x380.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-1024x380.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-300x111.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-768x285.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-1536x570.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="380" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4a1cJ9Y_X9Q" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4a1cj9y_x9q</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3HEEdlzT_7c" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3heedlzt_7c</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h5KYvJWuv_A" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/www.youtube.com/watch</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4uyHQIQqnWg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">？ www .youtube.com/watch？v = 4Uyhqiqqnwg</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZorebMKm5TM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zorebmkmkmkm5tm</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_x6FXjEU8ps" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://wwwww.youtube.com/watch?v=_xjeu8ps？</a></p><p> “ Hoku（Hoku）”是一个带有令人印象深刻的笑声和充满活力的声音的VTUBER。特征是不惧怕的沟通技巧以及全国人民的联系。</p><p>在日本的VTUBER机构中，无论公司或印度的规模如何，合作越来越普遍。但是，Hoku在这种环境之前拥有成功合作的记录，并且是这种先驱之一。</p><p> Hoku已与各种各样的团体合作，包括UP和Compaiming Indie Vtuber，“ Algorhorthm Project”，该组织目前被称为泰国的主要代理机构，印度尼西亚的“ Maha5”和“ Holove”和“ Holove”和“ Prism Project” 。 我是。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-1024x577.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-768x433.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-1536x866.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="577" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pIWR515faEg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=piwr515faeg</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1dF77Yti2hc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1df77yti2hc</a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8vefV8LsqSU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8vefv8lsqsu</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kJ0pN_tbfRI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kj0pn_tbfri</a></p><p> “ Zona（โซ）”是一名出色的歌手，并且作为一位站立的能力，他对语言具有积极的态度。我特别惊讶的是，她首次发行的原始歌曲“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pIWR515faEg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Memoria</a> ”是日语。</p><p>由于VTUBER是一种来自日本的文化，因此有讲述日语文化的观点，例如唱歌动漫和嗓音。结果，您通常可以看到Vtuber海外涵盖日本歌曲的场景。但是，在原始歌曲中，选择该国的语言是很常见的，在这方面，Zona的选择令人惊讶。</p><p>但是，我的想法立即被解雇了，原始歌曲“<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1dF77Yti2hc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">呼吸</a>”是泰语，而发行的“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8vefV8LsqSU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">reprise</a> ”是K-Pop风格的英语歌曲。这些多样化的音乐表达反映了泰国是一种“文化的文化”。</p><p>还有一种文化上传封面的歌曲翻译成粉丝的母语，例如“体育场恒星恒星”的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ULduRG1Gp_Q" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰国封面</a>。此外，Zona对语言的好奇心还以<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kJ0pN_tbfRI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">日语涵盖泰国流行歌曲</a>的态度。</p><p>我觉得这些活动源于该人的纯粹利益，超出了营销和战略。在日本广告牌的一篇文章中，据指出：“<a href="https://encount.press/archives/535529/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">即使日语和英语的歌词在将来也没有意义，这个时代也没有意义，</a> ”但是Zona的活动正是体现了预言的情况。是的。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1dhvfwo5iop5-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1dhvfwo5iop5-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 854px) 100vw, 854px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1dhvfwo5iop5-jpg.webp 854w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1dhvfwo5iop5-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1dhvfwo5iop5-768x432.webp 768w" width="854" height="480" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pTh_klItZTA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pth_klitzta</a></p><p> “ Fumi Hausu（Fumi Hausu（ฟูมิฟูมิ）”是属于Polygon项目的VTUBER，但具有非常独特的背景。最初，Fumi出生<a href="https://www.farmhouse.co.th/company/philosophy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">于1982年成立的</a>泰国食品公司“农舍”的知识产权（IP）。该公司与日本密切相关，例如出售名为“<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z-ongjmx7WE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">北海道牛奶风味面包</a>”的产品，并<a href="https://www.igloocg.com/portfolio/farmhouse/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">用日本叙事的3D动画广播广告</a>。因此，我相信这与Fumi的首次亮相背景有关，说：“ <a href="https://twitter.com/FumiHausu/status/1487351393854046211" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您有日本尼基吗？</a> ”</p><p>但是，Fumi突然毕业于2023年1月。毕业的原因不是一件泥泞的事情，而是 <a href="https://twitter.com/FumiHausu/status/1615349546225393667" target="_blank" rel="noopener">针对新的挑战和新挑战的</a>毕业，我的同事和粉丝们表示感谢。两个月后，Polygon Project <a href="https://twitter.com/Polygon_Project/status/1639258262984962051" target="_blank" rel="noopener">再次</a>制作了新的服装。有趣的是，Farmhouse仍使用名为Fumihausu的IP，并与Polygon项目<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GUlznh-H7SY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">保持良好的关系</a>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.fonoowmq3hm9-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.fonoowmq3hm9-1024x385.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.mogur