60w" width="1024" height="512" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1642884917003419648" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/vfestath/status/1642884917003419648</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1715338118109548736" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/vfestath/status/17153381095487366</a></p><p>早些时候，我将泰国作为Kizuna EI首次引起海外关注的国家之一。深厚连接的例子之一是“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GTa2HxIsBPM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kizuna ai最后一个现场“ Hello，World 2022”</a> ，这是Polygon Project成员<a href="https://twitter.com/LapinePLG/status/1491749802618490881" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lapine的参与</a>。这样，泰国的Kizuna AI的想法非常强烈，这种想法会导致更罕见的想法。这是一个基于Kizuna AI的动画，Kizuna AI，称为“ <a href="https://kizunanoallele.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kizuna的Allyl</a> ”，泰国Vtuber充当了泰国配音演员。</p><p>泰国<a href="https://twitter.com/jam_th_official/status/1472559907907911680" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vtuber有一个先例来配音动画</a>，但我真的很惊讶所有角色均已使用。此外，第二学期的所有配音演员都是Vtuber。作为一名作家，他从0开始看到Kizuna AI和国内和海外Vtuber，这代表了如此大胆的尊重的惊喜是最好的。</p><h3 id="h.1291u2ngbokl">开始使用动画MV的代理商</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-1024x572.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-1024x572.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-300x167.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-768x429.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-1536x857.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="572" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ECm0lLTjZxQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cm0lltjzxq</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VK5HWGOEJlU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vk5hwgoejlu</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8rnTRmG83Qw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://wwwww.youtube.com/www.youtube.com/watch?v=8rntrmg 83rntrmg 83qw</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kwyDbkZwgTE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https：// www .youtube.com/watch？v = kwydbkzwgte</a></p><p>另一个著名的泰国VTUBER代理商是“ <a href="https://www.pixela.me/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pixela Project</a> ”。该机构由“ <a href="https://www.matchlink.asia/business/page/Thailand/BANGKOK/43954-pixela-official-co-ltd.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pixela官方有限公司</a>”经营，首席执行官是“ <a href="https://twitter.com/Atarukun120" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ataru</a> ”，该公司以前管理过Yuchan。</p><p> Pixela Project的特征是，像Holo Live和Nijisanji这样的主要代理商，在首次亮相时发布了乐队原始歌曲的音乐视频（MV）。在早期，有许多日本风格的动漫角色，并且有许多MVS具有明亮而有趣的氛围，最近，MV具有更多的社交游戏角色和更多的黑暗氛围，结合了3D空间和2D插图。</p><h2 id="h.6xfripi0pcp6">在泰国令人兴奋的真实活动：VTUBER活动“ V-Festa”</h2><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.aa8pnw7pdhw3-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.aa8pnw7pdhw3-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.aa8pnw7pdhw3-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.aa8pnw7pdhw3-300x225.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.aa8pnw7pdhw3-768x576.webp 768w" width="800" height="600" /></a><br /> <a href="https://reviewspooh.com/v-festa-review/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://reviewspooh.com/v-festa-审查/</a></p><p>作为一个个人想法，我认为离线事件的存在对于主要在互联网上建立的VTUBER至关重要。意识到有一些有同样爱好的朋友，并享受享受真正聚会和兴奋的机会，这一点非常重要。这也是发现您尚不知道的VTUBER的绝佳机会。</p><p>在泰国，“ V-Festa”是第一个离线活动。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vmcqsxox150u-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vmcqsxox150u-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vmcqsxox150u-jpg.webp 900w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vmcqsxox150u-300x142.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vmcqsxox150u-768x364.webp 768w" width="900" height="426" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/ShoriNorimaki/status/1484885907262312452" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/shorinorimaki/status/1484885907262312452</a></p><p>该活动于2022年1月首次<a href="https://www.thailandtravel.or.jp/central-world/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在泰国首都曼谷的一家购物中心</a>举行。当时的VTubers在Meet＆Green活动中尚不为<a href="https://twitter.com/Ish_mond/status/1484884341448916997" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Aisha，Polygon Project</a>和Pixela项目<a href="https://twitter.com/7ofumus/status/1484484239143813122" target="_blank" rel="noopener">而闻名</a>。在此活动中，非常有趣的是，Ciel的原始歌曲“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V4L3YuhCUEY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vtuber One Enemens One Answer selps Introwuction</a> ”的模板在大屏幕上显示，并 <a href="https://twitter.com/VVinnie12/status/1485141328652804102" target="_blank" rel="noopener">作为VTubers的广告视频播放</a>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-1024x575.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="575" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1586748559411408897" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/vfestath/status/1586748591408897</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1660299412231553024" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/vfestath/status/status/16660294122223155533024</a> / <a href="https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1685130019163803648" target="_blank" rel="noopener">vfestath/</a><a href="https://twitter.com/Beam_haruka/status/1642008494546247680" target="_blank" rel="noopener">状态</a><a href="https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1685130019163803648" target="_blank" rel="noopener">/1685130019163803648</a></p><p>该活动定期举行，没有一次结束，我个人的印象是，这是泰国的VTUBER活动。通常，很难继续这样的事件，为什么可以定期持有它？这是因为<a href="https://reviewspooh.com/v-festa-review/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">托管了</a><a href="https://www.peerpower.co.th/blog/our-journey-with-shin-a-service" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><a href="https://www.gaai.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“</a> Shin-A Service”</a> 。</p><h2 id="h.xm30azgxcfw2">泰国著名的VTUBER是什么？</h2><p>在这里，我将捡起Vtuber，可以说这是泰国的一种不合理的Vtuber文化，特别是介绍了它的活跃方式。</p><h3 id="h.hdjyqljlzgwe">独立vtuber的崛起：Laibaht巧妙地操纵声音</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-1024x572.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-1024x572.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-300x167.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-768x429.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-1536x857.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="572" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xrWLzhw8inY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xrwlzhw8iny</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nb1fNtfBpj0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nb1fnb1fntfbpj0</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=egbo6T_toXY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/wath.youtube.com/watch</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ph6h5xmaRcQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">？ www .youtube.com/watch？v = ph6h5xmarcq</a></p><p>在泰国vtuber行业中，还有一些令人惊奇的事情是独奏，并在明星的楼梯上而不是小组活动。属于“ <a href="https://twitter.com/manyvproject" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Manybaht V Project</a> ”的“ Laibaht”就是其中之一。 Laibaht在声音和幽默中广受欢迎，主要是一个大胆的ASMR，炫耀了流行角色的声音和融合了Mome Neta的流行角色的声音。此外，封面歌曲已经发行，我个人喜欢“<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ph6h5xmaRcQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">我唱歌最好的九月</a>”，其中涵盖了“地球，风与火 -  9月”。在这首歌中，您可以感受到Laibaht的亮度，可爱和幽默感。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-1024x271.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-1024x271.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-300x80.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-768x204.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-1536x407.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="271" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1608464140879945728" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1608464140879945728</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1636326081329524737" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1636326081329524737</a></p><p>支持广告的一个指标是vtuber被爱的人。<a href="https://premium.kai-you.net/article/717" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在庆祝Vtuber的生日的活动中，还建立了</a>随着K-Pop趋势的全球范围内传播的欢呼广告。即使在泰国，这种文化也已经很普遍了，Vtuber的<a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1608464140879945728" target="_blank" rel="noopener">支持广告</a>也可以显示在MBK中心的巨大视野中。</p><p>此外，还举办了餐馆的协作活动，并支持各种形式，例如<a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1636326081329524737" target="_blank" rel="noopener">生活大小的面板</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1636326099230822401" target="_blank" rel="noopener">有限商品的分发</a>。除此之外，他还拥有翻译配音演员，莱巴特（Laibaht）负责主女主角艾科（ <a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1589582718308081666" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Eiko</a> Tsukimi）的作用，以及“儿童孩子”的<a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1666440826451378186" target="_blank" rel="noopener">阿里玛（Arima）的作用</a>。</p><h3 id="h.qtb2saxpbx9i">前进到e -sports：dtto。</h3><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-jpg.webp 1280w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3_nt4dN6gA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p3_nt4dn6ga</a></p><p> VTUBER是一个三语言，是国际VTUBER，在包括Apex Legends在内的FPS游戏中发挥了积极作用。在首次亮相时，他属于日本专业游戏团队“ Scarz”，<a href="https://www.scarz.net/news/cc_230915/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">合同到期</a>后，他暂时<a href="https://twitter.com/_dtto/status/1750479822386844148" target="_blank" rel="noopener">加入了“拒绝”</a> 。</p><p>他与Holo Holo Live的Haru Shibuya和Laplace Darkness合作，在日本众所周知。此外，由于它是在泰语中分发的，因此受到泰国许多球迷的支持。他还被<a href="https://twitter.com/Maruya_Event/status/1599773249877200902" target="_blank" rel="noopener">邀请</a>参加一个名为“ Maruya”的离线活动，活跃于泰国的Vtuber参加，并展示了他在泰国著名的。</p><p>除了FPS游戏外，我还发表了我在开始Vtuber活动之前唱歌的视频，其中包括歌曲“ <a href="https://youtu.be/HQ1zA2bbIRU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Glare</a> ”，以愉悦的声音演唱，声音和独特的柔和的声音，以令人愉悦的感觉完成听到。我推荐它。</p><h3 id="h.ytoqdtiw2jne">传播到音乐场景：没有唱歌的声音与灵魂产生共鸣</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-jpg.webp 1280w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gBNlpDTGck" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gbnlpdtgck</a></p><p>在泰国vtuber音乐界的背景下，“Unnämed（U-San）”是一位无法忽视的歌手。原创歌曲和封面歌曲具有强大而精致，并且在情感上演唱了许多作品，它们继续通过音乐吸引世界各地的粉丝。</p><p>我特别推荐的是与ARP的Dacapo合作的“ Ado -odo”的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gBNlpDTGck" target="_blank" rel="noopener">封面歌曲</a>。这首歌的最大吸引力是，才华横溢的歌手正在用自己的声音和最酷的声音互相打击。</p><p>此外，原始歌曲MV是最初是拳击的安排，但变为Muay Thai的世界观。这可能表明了对泰国ARP的尊重，而在<a href="https://www.dexerto.com/entertainment/unnamed-feature-u-san-vtuber-restart-2480915/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">采访</a>中说过的活跃于泰国的U-San的根源正在影响。</p><h2 id="h.94p14bb0fvfc">最热门的VTUBER小组“ Algorhorthm Project（ARP）”是什么？</h2><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vr8w748h5mo9-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vr8w748h5mo9-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 854px) 100vw, 854px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vr8w748h5mo9-jpg.webp 854w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vr8w748h5mo9-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vr8w748h5mo9-768x432.webp 768w" width="854" height="480" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6CbH6mUVPiw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cbh6muvpiw</a></p><p>一些VTUBER粉丝的利基市场专门从事利基市场。其中一个是<a href="https://note.com/mikan_ito" target="_blank" rel="noopener">热爱Vtuber音乐的</a><a href="https://note.com/mikan_ito" target="_blank" rel="noopener">粉丝</a>，而代理商的音乐开始成为<a href="https://note.com/showyoutaro/n/ndc5deed51bc3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">如此疯狂的Vtuber歌曲爱好者的传感器</a>。</p><p>该机构名称称为“ <a href="https://algorhythm.realic.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Algorhythm Project</a> （ARP）”。</p><p>我不是Vtuber的歌迷，热情的热情，但2022年仍然<a href="https://note.com/bluesura/n/n895d48b172bb" target="_blank" rel="noopener">沉浸在Vtuber的音乐中，在日本和海外都沉浸了一年</a>。特别是，我仍然记得，我对Solar的“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6CbH6mUVPiw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Solar Feat。@Selene_Arp-黎明</a>”感到震惊。歌唱的声音让人联想到虚拟歌手“ Hana No Ko” <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tMKrECxEpq8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">，有能力击败情绪</a>。让我写情感句子的另一个影响是，精心制作的动画具有丰富的独创性。</p><p>截至2022年，Vtuber歌曲已经拥有许多高质量的MV。在Holo Live中，“<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vV-5W7SFHDc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">宝藏海洋 - 我是您的宝藏盒</a>”在Nijisanji的“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=53jm_c2FMjw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vox Akuma -new Cydonia</a> ”中发布了美丽的动画MV，而“ <a href="https://kamitsubaki.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kamitsubaki Studio</a> ”是世界级别的水平。它以创意而闻名。然而，是一家尚不清楚海外的公司突然出现在这一热量MV中。此外，这款MV具有以某种方式“日语翻译歌词”，这是一项非常有趣的作品。</p><h3 id="h.19hzvwcgk7rv">用音乐的力量开辟一条新的道路的“算法”项目</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.7hoca8gh7k8b-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.7hoca8gh7k8b-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.7hoca8gh7k8b-jpg.webp 680w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.7hoca8gh7k8b-300x188.webp 300w" width="680" height="426" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber/status/1367474401587863555" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/arp_vtuber/status/1367474444015863555</a></p><p>它自己的语言存在的文化领域具有当地的音乐文化。由于日本有一个J-Pop，在韩国有K-Pop，因此泰国也被称为T-Pop，并具有自己的类型。泰国音乐场景是一个具有强烈音乐感的国家，因为传统音乐引起了人们的关注，但是新一代的音乐播放了数亿次。您会听到潜力，因为<a href="https://birthdayadjp.shop/blogs/birthday-ads/thai-ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">来自泰国的艺术家在K-Pop中活跃</a>。</p><p> ARP在这种泰国继续增长。该项目在“ <a href="https://algorhythm.realic.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Realic Production Co.，Ltd”中运行。</a>哲学是“<a href="https://algorhythm.realic.net/company/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">我们是创造力的人。虚拟YouTuber/Music Video/Motion Comic等。创建您的作品并填补您的梦想和想象力。</a> ”</p><p> ARP这个名字来自“算法”和“节奏”的综合词，并具有通过音乐节奏实现各种目标的意愿。除音乐外，具有个人才华的成员正在分发他们，这引起了兴奋。</p><h2 id="h.qjre8r7bs8mc">与ARP中其他VTUBER机构有何不同？</h2><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.i5p87xaq7yuo-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.i5p87xaq7yuo-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.i5p87xaq7yuo-jpg.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.i5p87xaq7yuo-300x90.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.i5p87xaq7yuo-768x230.webp 768w" width="1024" height="306" /></a><br /> <a href="https://algorhythm.realic.net/members" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://algorhythm.realic.net/members</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/LapisJellyF_ARP" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/lapisjellyf_arp</a></p><p>在VTUBER行业中，试镜倾向于以公共形式提高其才能。但是，ARP的特征<a href="https://pantip.com/topic/41928029" target="_blank" rel="noopener">是与此习俗相反</a>。 ARP不进行大型试镜， <a href="https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber/status/1570409854053023744" target="_blank" rel="noopener">直接侦察他们已经与机构和有才华的人才有关的创作者进行了</a>一些联系。</p><p>也许是由于这样的管理政策，成员之间的联系非常牢固，团队合作的良好在任何地方都闪耀。自从他开始活动以来，ARP已经进入了他的第四年，但此时还没有成员离开代理机构。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.esabrnnmca22-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.esabrnnmca22-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 922px) 100vw, 922px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.esabrnnmca22-jpg.webp 922w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.esabrnnmca22-300x151.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.esabrnnmca22-768x387.webp 768w" width="922" height="465" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6CbH6mUVPiw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cbh6muvpiw</a></p><p>另一个功能是ARP成员正在积极合作音乐制作。</p><p>例如，在ARP的第一个动漫风格的MV“ Dawn”中，作曲家和安排，人声编辑，桅杆，掌握，背部声音，字幕，日语翻译，日语翻译和VTUBER，他们在那之后首次亮相，首次亮相。我在工作。我在工作。此外，成员在评论部分印象深刻，表明他们是一部对发布充满热情的作品。</p><h3 id="h.yxjxd1rufbby">从MV可以看出的泰式手写动画制作</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.24oxbnmxzmlb-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.24oxbnmxzmlb-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.24oxbnmxzmlb-jpg.webp 600w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.24oxbnmxzmlb-300x240.webp 300w" width="600" height="480" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GhbpyfesrhQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ghbpyfesrhq</a></p><p>作为ARP的功能之一，我提到它是MV笔迹口味的动画，那么该动画来自哪里？</p><p>首先，泰国细胞动画和CG（计算机图形）动漫的历史是旧的，可​​以追溯到1950年代。据说<a href="https://artsandculture.google.com/story/payut-ngao-krachang-father-of-thai-animation-thai-film-archive/sAXhQtVXnGgZWQ?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰国细胞动画电影的先驱</a>是“ Payut Ngaokrachang”。 Payut曾在日本学习动画，并设计了一个摄像机架以用于细胞动画。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w3k7bcv6ng4e-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w3k7bcv6ng4e-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 854px) 100vw, 854px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w3k7bcv6ng4e-jpg.webp 854w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w3k7bcv6ng4e-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w3k7bcv6ng4e-768x432.webp 768w" width="854" height="480" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FF5vbODeHdk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ff5vbodehdk</a></p><p>但是，在泰国开发了多少手写动画，这是调查中没有很多杰出的作品。相反，CG动画似乎正在增长。这只是我的猜测，但我认为泰国动画市场是不稳定的，并且由于泰国在动画中源自日本以外的外国资本的影响。最近，Toho在“ <a href="https://www.igloocg.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Igloo Studio</a> ”中<a href="https://www.nikkei.com/nkd/disclosure/tdnr/20231102578098/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">投资</a>了总承包商，该承包商根据Netflix的原始小说制作了3D动画，并引起了日本的关注。</p><p>泰国动画行业是外包力量的原因之一是因素之一。但是，据说主要因素是泰国政府正在积极吸引外国公司，并<a href="https://www.absoluteanime.com/articles/how-thai-animators-have-helped-japans-anime-industry" target="_blank" rel="noopener">减少了动画领域对外国资本所有权的限制</a>。此外， <a href="https://sponsored.bloomberg.com/article/boi/creative-spark-ignites-thailands-digital-advance" target="_blank" rel="noopener">数字经济促进局（DEPA）正在促进数字化</a>，这使动画和游戏行业认真地增长。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-1024x492.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-1024x492.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-300x144.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-768x369.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-jpg.webp 1238w" width="1024" height="492" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/saratowga/status/1732637626237333706" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/saratowga/status/17326372626262373706</a></p><p>泰国大学还提供<a href="https://www.spu.ac.th/digitalmedia/programs/animation-and-visualeffects/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">专门研究CG动画的课程，</a>例如日本职业学校。作为这项倡议的一部分，还通过问候专业领域作为客座讲师的专业领域的技术人员与学生分享。当然，负责ARP MV动画的创作者也在曼谷的历史悠久的坟墓大学 <a href="https://twitter.com/saratowga/status/1732637626237333706" target="_blank" rel="noopener">讲座</a>。</p><p>有几个创建ARP动画的创作者，尤其是Evalia的“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f_gN2-_UZIs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ค（无尽的回声）</a> ”视频导演Kago，泰语动画师Kago，他还在日本动画行业中取得了纪录。我在这里。 Kago在2023年还活跃于<a href="https://twitter.com/_kakakakago/status/1742326082429456848" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“偶像大师灰姑娘女孩”</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/_kakakakago/status/1737803716026364337" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“ Uma Musume Pretty Derby”</a>的关键动画师（原始图纸）。</p><p>在ARP发行的50多首原创歌曲中，有10多首手绘动画增加了，参与制作的泰语创作者逐渐增加，而Kago和其他人则专门从事<a href="https://twitter.com/_kakakakago/status/1755694947972567086" target="_blank" rel="noopener">动画动画</a>。机构的规模。</p><h3 id="h.1bv4vz2dcjxl">对支持ARP核心的首席执行官“真实”的内容的热情</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-1024x369.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-1024x369.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-300x108.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-768x277.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-1536x554.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="369" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber/status/1610639907843723264" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/arp_vtuber/status/16106399907843723264</a><br /> <a href="https://youtube.com/watch?v=WmEOkpC6IrQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://youtube.com/watch?v=wmeokpc6irq</a></p><p>支持ARP的主要角色之一是<a href="https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Real</a> ，这是现实制作的首席执行官。 ARP成员熟悉“红鸭”的昵称，并且经常被爱，例如在Twitter上经常有趣，<a href="https://youtube.com/watch?v=WmEOkpC6IrQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">出现在MV上</a>，并<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BVA1c7fPfCg" target="_b